blog.title: House Of Max
blog.description: Welcome to the first ever full Max appreciation blog. It’s been done with every other Pokémon character, so let’s focus on the little-known underrated character, Max, for a change. Enjoy the first blog of this kind. Also, Max X Bonnie forever!!!

summary:
Max: Bonnie! A Pokémon is over there! (points slightly left from where the Pokémon he found is) 
Bonnie: Uh, actually, it’s over...
body:
Max: Bonnie! A Pokémon is over there! (points slightly left from where the Pokémon he found is)

Bonnie: Uh, actually, it’s over there, Max. (points to the Pokémon’s actual location)

Max: Oh… sorry, Bonnie. Just a little hard to see without glasses.
